snippet.title: A Tiny Sticker Tale - Official Gameplay Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2023 Showcase
snippet.description: Here’s a look at gameplay in the charming world of A Tiny Sticker Tale in this trailer for the upcoming relaxing adventure game about taking and placing anything from the world as stickers. A Tiny Sticker Tale is coming to PC and Nintendo Switch, and a Kickstarter campaign is available now.
